desc: Healing and professional massage therapy with facials in the International Market Place. The mall is in the center of Waikiki, and we're located on the ground floor, near the Kuhio Ave entrance, across from Sachs 5th Avenue. We provide massage from Swedish to Shiatsu, Deep Tissue to Reflexology, facials, and more.
